### 1. Get all requests
GET http://localhost:3000/api/requests
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Create a new gate pass request (Student)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentName": "Gourav Vishwakarma",
  "rollNumber": "21A51A0501",
  "reason": "Going home for emergency",
  "dateTime": "2025-10-25 14:30"
}

### 3. Get only pending requests
GET http://localhost:3000/api/requests/pending
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Approve a request (replace ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/requests/REQUEST_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "approved",
  "remarks": "Approved for valid reason"
}

### 5. Reject a request (replace ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/requests/REQUEST_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "rejected",
  "remarks": "Invalid reason provided"
}

### 6. Scan an approved pass (replace ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/scan/REQUEST_ID
Content-Type: application/json
